Complete rewrite of the parsing engine in Net_Ping_Result class. Changed
from using a separate parser for each "sysname" as inferred from the
OS_Guess module, to one very generalized output parser which can parse
many (dare I say 'all'?) different ping output formats (including language
localizations.) Note that there is now a more powerful test suite in
the tests/ subdirectory that exercises the new parser against a large
set of sample ping outputs.
